00:23:06,294 --> 00:23:08,394
那邊有些神槍手 專門打這樣的人
They got sharpshooters that are trained to look for them.

325
00:23:08,464 --> 00:23:10,494
他們知道 如果他們幹掉一個醫務兵
And they know that if they take out a corpsman

326
00:23:10,564 --> 00:23:13,034
好多士兵就會缺乏救助而死 明白麼？
another dozen Marines will die unattended. All right?

327
00:23:13,104 --> 00:23:14,434
好的 麥克
Okay, Mike.

328
00:23:21,144 --> 00:23:22,634
好 就停在這兒
Yeah, right there.

329
00:23:53,644 --> 00:23:55,904
把門關上  看在上帝份上
Close the damn door. For God's sake.

330
00:23:55,984 --> 00:23:58,104
哈 說得好像那樣就沒事了一樣
Yeah, like that's gonna help.

331
00:24:04,424 --> 00:24:06,254
那是你女朋友麼 酋長？
That your girlfriend, Chief?

332
00:24:08,254 --> 00:24:10,854
肯定是個超級印第安美女
Bet she's a pretty damn good-looking squaw.

333
00:24:10,924 --> 00:24:14,454
你肯定想你女朋友 還有你們溫暖的小窩棚了
Bet you're missing her, and that little wigwam of yours.

334
00:24:23,904 --> 00:24:26,874
（日方廣播）歡迎 來硫磺島 作客的陸戰隊員們
Welcome, all Marines off lwo Jima.

335
00:24:27,544 --> 00:24:29,474
我們期待已久…
We have a long-time wait...

336
00:24:29,544 --> 00:24:31,844
看看他們對犯人都做了些什麼
It's what they do to prisoners,

337
00:24:35,054 --> 00:24:38,024
這還算是好的 老天
at least the lucky ones. Jesus.

338
00:24:38,994 --> 00:24:43,894
牛仔 我要是你 才不會舉白旗呢
If I were you, cowpokes, I wouldn't think about waving a white bandanna.

339
00:24:43,964 --> 00:24:48,484
（日方廣播）可憐的陸戰隊員們 無緣無故  離家千里
Poor Marines, so far from home for no good reason.

340
00:24:49,804 --> 00:24:53,294
想想家中苦苦期盼的女友…
Think of your girls back home, waiting for you.

341
00:24:53,374 --> 00:24:56,364
但女孩孤身一人  怎能熬過 漫漫長夜
But a girl cannot stay home every night.

342
00:24:56,444 --> 00:24:59,604
想一想 她們今晚會和誰同床共枕？
So who do you think they're with tonight?

343
00:25:00,444 --> 00:25:05,344
她會讓他吻她麼？ 他會在你的葬禮上去安慰她麼？
And will she let him kiss her? And will he comfort her at your funeral?

344
00:25:05,814 --> 00:25:10,184
這段甜美的音樂可以讓你們 想起家中的女友
This sweet music is to make you think of your girls back home

345
00:25:10,254 --> 00:25:12,344
苦苦思念你們的女友
who are missing you.

346
00:25:12,424 --> 00:25:15,324
本日節目到此結束 明晚再會
This is all for now. I'll see you tomorrow night.

347
00:27:32,024 --> 00:27:33,184
士兵們！
Gunners!

348
00:27:40,104 --> 00:27:43,034
行動！行動！ 衝上防波堤！
Move, let's go! Let's go, get up on the berm!

349
00:27:50,184 --> 00:27:51,704
士兵們！
Gunners!

350
00:28:02,794 --> 00:28:04,524
安全！
We're clear!

351
00:28:07,594 --> 00:28:09,194
衝上防波堤！
Get up the berm!

352
00:28:11,634 --> 00:28:13,694
貝克連 行動！
Baker Company, move out!

353
00:28:13,774 --> 00:28:15,394
看到二排了麼? 沒有
Seen Second Platoon? I don't see them.

354
00:28:15,474 --> 00:28:16,994
一班！行動！
First Squad, move it out!

355
00:28:17,074 --> 00:28:18,734
天 這地方真臭
God, this place reeks.

356
00:28:32,454 --> 00:28:34,754
上上上！ 行動！
Go, go, go! Move out!

357
00:28:34,824 --> 00:28:39,784
上上上！ 上上上！ 丟掉背包！上！
Go, go, go, go! Go, go! Go! Go, go! Drop your packs! Go!

358
00:28:40,964 --> 00:28:42,294
安全！
All clear!

359
00:28:46,104 --> 00:28:48,434
天 你忙活什麼呢? 他走丟了
Jesus, you needed some exercise? He got lost.

360
00:28:48,504 --> 00:28:51,274
一百艘登陸艇衝上一個海灘 這傢伙走丟了
A hundred landing craft heading for one beach and this guy gets lost.

361
00:28:51,344 --> 00:28:53,364
我們居然幹出這種好事來 天 一團糟
Now I'm glad we did. Jesus, what a mess.

362
00:28:54,074 --> 00:28:56,514
他們為什麼不開火？
Any theories why they ain't shooting?

363
00:28:57,684 --> 00:28:59,744
我都快變神經質了
It's getting on my nerves.

364
00:28:59,814 --> 00:29:01,874
可能他們全死了吧
Maybe they're all dead.

365
00:29:02,354 --> 00:29:05,374
你怎麼看 醫生？ 你認為他們全死了麼？
What do you think, Doc? You think they're all dead?

366
00:29:28,714 --> 00:29:31,844
麥克 叫上六個人 把那門炮運到海灘上
Mike, take six men and bring that gun onto the beach.

367
00:29:31,914 --> 00:29:35,244
二排 行動！ 保持低姿 前進
Second Platoon, let's move out! Stay down. Come on.

368
00:29:35,754 --> 00:29:37,514
行動 行動！
Move! Move!

369
00:30:15,124 --> 00:30:17,094
臥倒！ 找掩護！
Get down! Take cover!

370
00:30:18,394 --> 00:30:19,724
行動！
Move out!

371
00:30:43,554 --> 00:30:45,574
火力掩護！ 持續壓制！
Cover fire! Pour it on!

372
00:30:48,394 --> 00:30:51,554
雷  趕快把火力轉向右側！
Ray, shift your fire to the right, now!

373
00:31:00,974 --> 00:31:02,164
醫務兵！
Corpsman!

374
00:31:04,204 --> 00:31:07,474
我先給你固定手臂 然後再來給你止痛！
I'm gonna sling your arm and then I'll give you a shot for the pain!

375
00:31:08,444 --> 00:31:10,774
行動！行動！離開灘頭！
Move, move! Off the beach!

376
00:31:10,844 --> 00:31:12,504
找掩護！
Take cover!

377
00:31:29,804 --> 00:31:31,424
你在家埵陪茪k朋友 是吧？
You got a girl back home, Marine?

378
00:31:31,504 --> 00:31:34,164
我們肯定能讓你見到她 好麼？
We're gonna make sure she sees you, all right?

379
00:31:34,234 --> 00:31:36,724
壓住這個傷口！
I need pressure on this wound!

380
00:31:44,084 --> 00:31:45,944
都是從哪堨捶茠滿H
Where's the fire coming from?

381
00:31:56,724 --> 00:31:58,454
他們在哪？
Where are they?

382
00:31:59,294 --> 00:32:01,524
注意看槍口焰  朝那兒打！
Look for a flash, shoot at it!

383
00:32:02,704 --> 00:32:04,034
我們上 我們…
Let's go, let...

384
00:32:21,854 --> 00:32:24,154
12點鐘方向 幹掉那個碉堡
Twelve o'clock, take out the bunker!

385
00:32:25,354 --> 00:32:26,654
你完了！
You're over!

386
00:32:37,034 --> 00:32:39,294
三班 衝上去 行動！
Third Squad, forward! Move!

387
00:32:50,784 --> 00:32:52,644
他們在哪 長官?
Where are they, sir?

388
00:32:52,714 --> 00:32:55,844
10點方向有一個！ 十點方向 暗堡一個 中士！
We got ten o'clock! Ten o'clock, pillbox! Sergeant!

389
00:32:57,424 --> 00:33:00,044
中士！ 我能拿下它 什麼？
Sergeant! I think I can clear that out. What?

390
00:33:00,124 --> 00:33:01,754
好  你去吧 給
All right, you go. Here.

391
00:33:01,824 --> 00:33:04,554
拿著 檢查武器
Take these. Check your weapon.

392
00:33:04,624 --> 00:33:06,524
好了？上！掩護！
Yeah? Go! Cover!

393
00:33:06,594 --> 00:33:07,994
掩護他！
Cover him!

394
00:33:14,034 --> 00:33:15,504
掩護 掩護！
Cover, cover!

395
00:33:21,044 --> 00:33:22,564
婊子養的
Son-of-a-bitch.

396
00:33:27,684 --> 00:33:29,274
我們上 上！
Let's go! Go!

397
00:33:29,354 --> 00:33:30,714
行動！
Move it out!

398
00:33:33,954 --> 00:33:35,584
上上上！
Go, go, go!

399
00:33:38,594 --> 00:33:40,254
臥倒 臥倒 臥倒！
Down, down, down!

400
00:33:59,044 --> 00:34:00,344
清除
It's clear.

401
00:34:00,414 --> 00:34:01,814
幹得好
Good work.

402
00:34:10,264 --> 00:34:11,854
你不是說清除了麼？
I thought you said it was clear!

403
00:34:11,924 --> 00:34:13,294
剛才是這樣！
It was!

404
00:34:19,104 --> 00:34:22,334
靠 估計是又換人了
Shit, I guess they're not in there firing at us then.

405
00:34:23,674 --> 00:34:25,144
林勃！
Lindberg!

406
00:34:25,204 --> 00:34:26,334
到！
Yeah!

407
00:34:26,414 --> 00:34:27,904
燒了它！
Light it up!

408
00:34:31,044 --> 00:34:32,314
艾斯 我掩護你！
I'll cover you, Ice!

409
00:34:32,384 --> 00:34:36,284
掩護個屁！ 已經有這麼多人在開槍了！
Don't cover shit! There's already enough people shooting!

410
00:34:36,354 --> 00:34:39,444
中一槍我就變成火人了
One bullet and this thing goes up like a Roman candle!

411
00:34:39,524 --> 00:34:41,584
上！ 停火！
Go! Shift fire!

412
00:34:41,654 --> 00:34:42,924
大家停火！
Shift your fire!

413
00:34:42,994 --> 00:34:45,354
上 上！ 大家停火！
Go, go! Shift your fire!

414
00:34:45,664 --> 00:34:47,894
大家停火！
Shift your fire!

415
00:34:53,434 --> 00:34:55,304
上！ 行動！
Go! Move it out!

416
00:35:22,494 --> 00:35:25,194
目標清除！ 保持低姿！ 等待支援！
Hit the deck! Stay down! Wait for support!

417
00:35:26,474 --> 00:35:28,734
真是一場惡戰
Is this a bad battle or what?

418
00:35:28,804 --> 00:35:30,864
是他媽一場屠殺
It's a fucking slaughter.

419
00:35:41,814 --> 00:35:43,514
老天
Christ Jesus!

420
00:35:50,394 --> 00:35:53,324
馬上叫一個機槍小組過來！
Get a machine gun team set up over here, now!

421
00:35:58,204 --> 00:36:00,134
謝天謝地！ 坦克！
Thank God! Tanks!

422
00:36:00,204 --> 00:36:03,134
通信兵！把坦克叫過來！
Runner! Get those tanks up here!

423
00:36:04,974 --> 00:36:06,234
我靠
Oh, shit.

424
00:36:06,844 --> 00:36:08,144
臥倒！
Get down!

425
00:36:08,714 --> 00:36:11,014
下士 注意左翼！
Corporal, watch your left flank!

426
00:36:11,084 --> 00:36:14,344
沒坦克我們也得上！ 行動！ 行動！
Let's go without them! Move out! Move out!

427
00:36:41,474 --> 00:36:43,874
伊基 你那邊抬起來一點 他快掉下來了
Iggy, you gotta lift your side, he's gonna roll off.

428
00:36:43,944 --> 00:36:45,384
知道了 醫生！
Got it, Doc!

429
00:36:48,584 --> 00:36:49,884
炮彈來襲！
Incoming!

430
00:36:55,694 --> 00:36:57,784
上 上 上 上！
Move, move, move, move!

431
00:37:25,724 --> 00:37:27,214
不要停！
Keep moving!

432
00:37:27,294 --> 00:37:29,954
把那輛履帶式登陸車弄上岸！
Get that LVT up on the beach!

433
00:37:31,324 --> 00:37:32,654
不要停！
Keep moving!

434
00:37:38,804 --> 00:37:40,924
老弟 下一個就輪到你了 我們會帶你離開這堛
You're next, pal, we're getting you out of here.

435
00:37:45,474 --> 00:37:46,774
行動！
Move it!

436
00:38:01,694 --> 00:38:03,024
有好消息
Great news.

437
00:38:04,464 --> 00:38:08,364
你在塔拉瓦營地先過好才有可能 因為我們就要去那兒
Maybe if you live up on Camp Tarawa, 'cause that's where we're headed.

438
00:38:09,964 --> 00:38:11,264
不是關於你和我的
Not you and me.

439
00:38:11,334 --> 00:38:13,864
賽佛倫斯上尉問我 還有誰在那張照片上
Captain Severance asked me who else was in that picture,

440
00:38:13,934 --> 00:38:15,704
我就說 老天 我怎麼想得起來
and Christ if I could remember,

441
00:38:15,774 --> 00:38:18,864
但是當時有麥克 醫生 富蘭克林 我 還有漢克·漢森
but it was Mike and Doc and Franklin and me and Hank Hansen

442
00:38:18,944 --> 00:38:21,674
而且我對他說你當時也在那兒
but I just remembered, you were there, too.

443
00:38:26,754 --> 00:38:28,244
我不在那兒
I wasn't there.

444
00:38:28,314 --> 00:38:29,844
但你在那之前在
'Course you were.

445
00:38:29,924 --> 00:38:32,384
漢克也不在 他升的是第一面旗
Neither was Hank. He raised the first flag.

446
00:38:32,454 --> 00:38:34,254
那面旗子是哈倫·布勞克升起來的
It was Harlon Block that raised that one.

447
00:38:34,324 --> 00:38:37,154
靠 我都跟他們說那是漢克了
Shit. I told them it was Hank.

448
00:38:37,964 --> 00:38:40,694
你當時又不在那兒 聰明蛋 你怎麼知道是哈倫？
You weren't there, Mr. Smart Ass, how'd you know it was Harlon?

449
00:38:40,764 --> 00:38:43,464
你跟他們說了有我麼？ 沒有 我就跟他們說我記得有你
You tell them it was me? No. Like I said, I just remembered.

450
00:38:43,534 --> 00:38:45,524
很好 閉嘴吧
Good, keep your mouth shut.

451
00:38:46,004 --> 00:38:48,264
他們知道照片上還有別人的 一眼便知
They know there was somebody else, you can see it in the picture.

452
00:38:48,334 --> 00:38:49,434
那你找個死人頂上吧
Then pick someone dead.

453
00:38:49,504 --> 00:38:51,304
他們可不想要死人 你個蠢紅番
They don't want somebody dead, you dumb redskin,

454
00:38:51,374 --> 00:38:53,774
他們想把我們運回國
they want to ship us back to the States.

455
00:38:54,244 --> 00:38:56,004
我跟你說什麼了？
What did I tell you?

456
00:38:58,484 --> 00:39:00,004
我說我不在那兒！
I wasn't there.

457
00:39:00,084 --> 00:39:01,574
聽見沒？ 好吧
You hear? All right.

458
00:39:02,384 --> 00:39:04,014
冷靜點
Just settle down.

459
00:39:05,224 --> 00:39:08,384
我哪兒也不去 你哪兒也不去
I'm not going anywhere. You're not going anywhere.

460
00:39:25,954 --> 00:39:28,954
埃尼威托克（美國托管地）1945年4月


461
00:39:44,424 --> 00:39:46,154
誰說的？
Who the hell says?

462
00:39:50,234 --> 00:39:52,064
淨胡扯
This is horseshit.

463
00:39:55,674 --> 00:39:57,294
你受傷了？
You wounded, son?

464
00:39:57,674 --> 00:39:58,864
沒有 長官
No, sir.

465
00:39:58,944 --> 00:40:02,604
那你赤手空拳殺過日本鬼子麼？
Well, did you take out a nest of Japs butt-naked with your bare hands?

466
00:40:02,674 --> 00:40:05,734
你要是那麼幹過 我就把這個座位讓給你坐
'Cause if I'm gonna give up my seat to a hero

467
00:40:05,814 --> 00:40:07,684
你最好能有點傳奇故事可講的
he better have a good goddamn story to tell.

468
00:40:07,754 --> 00:40:09,114
沒有 長官
No, sir.

469
00:40:09,184 --> 00:40:12,814
那你好自為之 因為聖誕節之前 你就會被遺忘的
Then enjoy it, 'cause they'll forget you before Christmas.

470
00:40:38,614 --> 00:40:41,144
第六人（指升旗隊列中） 你知道其餘人的名字麼？
The sixth man, you got a name?

471
00:40:41,214 --> 00:40:43,274
抱歉 還是記不起來
Sorry, still don't remember.

472
00:40:43,354 --> 00:40:46,984
那還真是丟臉了 我跟上面保證過你知道他是誰的
It's a damn shame, 'cause I promised the Major you'd know who it was.

473
00:40:47,054 --> 00:40:49,184
你要是再說不出來
Fact, you not knowing throws a doubt on you

474
00:40:49,254 --> 00:40:51,524
你就很難讓人相信你自己 也是升旗手之一了
being one of the flag-raisers yourself.

475
00:40:51,594 --> 00:40:54,424
乾脆大家都別尷尬 你一著陸
Since no one wants to be embarrassed, the moment you land

476
00:40:54,494 --> 00:40:56,364
他們就把你送回衝繩島去
they'll turn you around, ship you off to Okinawa

477
00:40:56,434 --> 00:40:59,124
在海灘上跟你的兄弟們見面
in time to meet your buddies on the beach.

478
00:40:59,204 --> 00:41:02,834
所以 你還跟我兜什麼圈子 名字告訴我
So, why don't you stop screwing with me? Give me a damn name.

479
00:41:21,054 --> 00:41:23,544
讓路！ 讓路！ 走開 走開！ 讓路！
Gangway! Gangway! Let's go, let's go! Gangway!

480
00:41:23,624 --> 00:41:27,224
那婊子養的跑哪去了? 海因斯！ 海因斯?
Where the hell is that son-of-a-bitch? Hayes! Hayes?

481
00:41:27,734 --> 00:41:29,494
海因斯你個紅鬼 趕緊給我過來！
Hayes, get your red ass over here!

482
00:41:29,564 --> 00:41:31,434
搞得我好像在自己眼皮底下
Make me look like I don't know what my own men are doing

483
00:41:31,504 --> 00:41:33,664
都不知道自己手下的人埵陪 升旗手似的
with a flag the size of my mother's house?

484
00:41:33,734 --> 00:41:35,674
他媽的 艾拉 你不該對我撒謊
God damn it, Ira, you shouldn't have lied to me.

485
00:41:35,734 --> 00:41:38,034
你讓我看起來像個白癡
You made me look like a complete asshole.

486
00:41:38,104 --> 00:41:40,904
我們在這兒會想你的 好運
We're gonna miss you around here. Good luck.

487
00:41:47,654 --> 00:41:49,984
現在你的名字也上報紙了
Now your name's in the paper, too.

488
00:41:54,354 --> 00:41:57,484
你的醫生剛才說 我們要推遲你的手術
Just heard your doctor say we're postponing your operation.

489
00:41:57,564 --> 00:41:59,654
你會被運回國的
You're being shipped back to the mainland.

490
00:41:59,724 --> 00:42:03,664
每個看過照片的人都以為 插旗就意味著勝利
Everybody who saw that picture thought planting the flag meant victory.

491
00:42:04,764 --> 00:42:07,464
他們只想知道那個 勝利
That's all they wanted to know. Victory.

492
00:42:08,474 --> 00:42:12,734
那張照片照了幾個星期以後 照片堶惜@半的人就都死了
Within a few weeks of that picture being taken, half the men in it were dead.

493
00:42:12,804 --> 00:42:16,644
漢森太太！ 漢森太太！ 您知道漢克是個英雄麼?
Mrs. Hansen! Mrs. Hansen! Did you know Hank was a hero?

494
00:42:16,714 --> 00:42:18,844
您為他自豪麼 漢森太太? 他年少時品行如何?
Are you proud of him, Mrs. Hansen? What was he like as a boy?

495
00:42:18,914 --> 00:42:20,004
請看這 太太
Look this way, please, ma'am.

496
00:42:20,084 --> 00:42:21,314
對您的兒子您有何評價?
What do you have to say about your son?

497
00:42:23,854 --> 00:42:26,914
但成為照片中的一員頗有意義
But somehow being a part of it meant something.

498
00:42:27,724 --> 00:42:32,424
看著它 你就會相信 所有的犧牲並非白費
Looking at it, you could believe their sacrifice was not a waste.

499
00:42:36,934 --> 00:42:39,864
是啊 我也可以想像那就是哈倫
Yeah, I might have thought that was Harlon, too.

500
00:42:39,934 --> 00:42:41,094
本來就是
It is.

501
00:42:42,634 --> 00:42:46,044
貝爾 他們的名字就列在這兒 那不是他
Belle, their names are right here. It's not him.

502
00:42:47,114 --> 00:42:51,744
要不是你 他現在就會好好地活著 坐在這
And he would be alive and sitting right here if it wasn't for you.

503
00:42:52,484 --> 00:42:56,074
看照片的時候你自己多想想吧 埃德
You think about that when you look at his picture, Ed.

504
00:44:03,704 --> 00:44:06,074
我得趕緊回家換衣服
And I need to rush home and change

505
00:44:06,144 --> 00:44:10,004
因為一會兒有一個州長的宴會 然後還有一個遊行
because there's the Governor's banquet and then there's the parade.

506
00:44:10,074 --> 00:44:13,304
想想看 州長親自來這堥ㄖ畯
Imagine, the Governor is coming here to meet us.

507
00:44:13,384 --> 00:44:15,214
現在我穿的是藍色 那麼如果…
Now, I'm wearing blue so, if...

508
00:44:15,284 --> 00:44:17,514
你也要去換衣服麼? 現在我們打斷正在播出的節目
Are you going to change? We interrupt this program to bring you

509
00:44:17,584 --> 00:44:19,104
播出一則由哥倫比亞廣播公司 世界新聞節目帶來的最新消息
a special news bulletin from CBS World News.

510
00:44:19,184 --> 00:44:23,214
一家通訊社剛剛宣佈 羅斯福總統已經去世
A press association has just announced that President Roosevelt is dead.

511
00:44:23,294 --> 00:44:25,854
總統死於腦溢血
The President died of a cerebral hemorrhage.

512
00:44:25,924 --> 00:44:30,294
就目前所知 總統死於佐治亞州 溫泉療養院
All we know so far is that the President died at Warm Springs in Georgia.

513
00:44:31,594 --> 00:44:33,894
更多信息將每小時送出
Further updates every hour.

514
00:44:34,064 --> 00:44:36,264
今日氣溫保持穩定
Temperatures will remain the same today,

515
00:44:36,334 --> 00:44:39,204
35度到40度出頭 天氣晴朗…
in the mid-30s to low 40s with clear skies.

516
00:44:39,274 --> 00:44:40,574
喂?
Hello?

517
00:44:41,304 --> 00:44:43,404
好的 當然
Yes. Of course.

518
00:44:44,174 --> 00:44:47,304
不 我們能理解 那確實不太合適
No, we understand. It wouldn't be right.

519
00:44:49,344 --> 00:44:50,684
謝謝
Thank you.

520
00:44:54,524 --> 00:44:57,684
先生們 他來了 參議員博伊德先生、參議員羅布森先生
Here he is, gentlemen. Senator Boyd, Senator Robson.

521
00:44:57,754 --> 00:45:01,454
參議員哈迪根先生 這是一等兵艾拉·海因斯
Senator Haddigan. I'd like you to meet Private First Class Ira Hayes.

522
00:45:01,564 --> 00:45:03,464
見到你真太好了
Damn good to meet you.

523
00:45:03,534 --> 00:45:05,894
認識你真令人自豪
Proud to make your acquaintance, son.

524
00:45:10,704 --> 00:45:11,864
你說什麼?
Sorry?

525
00:45:13,774 --> 00:45:16,504
那是皮馬族印第安語啊 你難道聽不懂自己的母語麼？
That's Pima Indian talk, boy, don't you know your own language?

526
00:45:16,574 --> 00:45:19,204
費了好大勁才學會這一句
Took forever to memorize the damn gibberish.

527
00:45:19,274 --> 00:45:22,804
抱歉 參議員先生 我離開 皮馬族保留地已經很久了
Sorry, I've been away from the reservation too long, Senator.

528
00:45:28,724 --> 00:45:30,054
醫生 艾拉
Doc. Ira.

529
00:45:30,124 --> 00:45:33,094
現在有請 硫磺島的英雄們！
And now, the heroes of lwo Jima!

530
00:45:33,164 --> 00:45:36,424
該你們了 上 上 上 上 上
That's you. Go, go, go, go. Go.

531
00:45:36,494 --> 00:45:38,194
請大家歡迎
Please welcome

532
00:45:38,894 --> 00:45:42,524
海軍醫務兵約翰·佈雷德利
Navy Corpsman John "Doc" Bradley,

533
00:45:43,774 --> 00:45:47,224
一等兵艾拉·海因斯
Private First Class Ira Hayes,

534
00:45:48,604 --> 00:45:52,564
一等兵瑞尼·蓋格南
Private First Class Rene Gagnon!

535
00:46:22,174 --> 00:46:25,004
真他媽壯觀
Holy shit.

536
00:46:25,614 --> 00:46:28,584
請進 請進 請進 我是巴德·葛博 財政部的
Come in, come in, come in. Bud Gurber, Treasury Department.

537
00:46:28,644 --> 00:46:30,274
瑞尼·蓋格南 巴德·葛博
Rene Gagnon. Bud Gurber.

538
00:46:30,384 --> 00:46:33,014
帶他們四處轉過了麼? 剛看了場精綵球賽
You showing the boys the sights? We saw a hell of a ball game.

539
00:46:33,084 --> 00:46:35,384
很好 酒在那兒 自己倒吧
That's great. The bar's there, help yourself.

540
00:46:35,454 --> 00:46:37,424
我給你們準備了幾張簡易的表格
I got some briefing sheets for you here,

541
00:46:37,494 --> 00:46:39,324
上面有一些我們想讓你們說的話
just some simple things we want you to say.

542
00:46:39,394 --> 00:46:42,884
概括起來就是「買債券吧」 不過別說太頻繁了
Mostly, "Buy bonds," can't say that too often.

543
00:46:42,964 --> 00:46:45,124
你們的日程表一直在改
Itineraries, those are changing every couple minutes.

544
00:46:45,194 --> 00:46:47,684
人人都想見你們
Everybody wants to meet you guys.

545
00:46:47,764 --> 00:46:51,134
不少女人寄來裝著長襪的信封
I got women sending up envelopes with stockings in them,

546
00:46:51,204 --> 00:46:54,434
還有用口紅寫的小紙條 這事可別外傳了 對吧？
notes written in lipstick. We won't mention that to the press, am I right?

547
00:46:54,504 --> 00:46:56,974
看在上帝份上 喝一杯
Have a drink, for Christ's sake.

548
00:46:57,044 --> 00:46:59,414
老天 你們剛才也都看到了吧
My God, what you boys must have seen over there.

549
00:46:59,474 --> 00:47:01,174
我一直在關注著新聞
I've been watching the newsreels.

550
00:47:01,244 --> 00:47:03,874
老天 我們有的忙了
Jesus Christ, that was a fight and a half.

551
00:47:04,884 --> 00:47:08,844
我們要籌到大筆的錢 時間卻不充裕
So, we got a hell of a lot of money to raise, not a lot of time.

552
00:47:08,924 --> 00:47:10,984
明天先去白宮 然後領你們到處轉轉
White House tomorrow, then we trot you over

553
00:47:11,054 --> 00:47:12,614
去跟一大堆國會議員握手
to shake hands with a couple of hundred Congressmen

554
00:47:12,694 --> 00:47:14,214
全是些一毛不拔的鐵公雞
who won't pull a penny out of their pockets.

555
00:47:14,294 --> 00:47:15,554
政客都是好演員
Politicians and actors.

556
00:47:15,624 --> 00:47:16,724
你把他們放到一個飯館
You put them in a restaurant together,

557
00:47:16,794 --> 00:47:18,694
他們等到自己老死 都不會有人付賬
they'd die of old age before picking up the check.

558
00:47:18,764 --> 00:47:21,704
下一站是紐約 時代廣場
Then New York City, Times Square,

559
00:47:21,764 --> 00:47:24,764
與社會名流共進晚餐 然後就是芝加哥…
dinners with various hoi polloi, then Chicago...

560
00:47:24,834 --> 00:47:26,734
這些「金星母親」是什麼人？
Who are these "Gold Star Mothers"?

561
00:47:26,804 --> 00:47:30,034
那是我們對那些已死的升旗手 母親們的稱呼
That's what we're calling the mothers of the dead flag-raisers.

562
00:47:30,114 --> 00:47:31,974
你們遞給每個母親一面旗子
You present each mother with a flag,

563
00:47:32,044 --> 00:47:34,574
然後說幾句話 人們就會慷慨解囊
they say a few words, people will shit money.

564
00:47:34,644 --> 00:47:36,174
多感人啊
It'll be so moving.

565
00:47:36,244 --> 00:47:38,944
但這埵竟~克·漢森的媽媽
But this says Hank Hansen's mom.

566
00:47:39,014 --> 00:47:41,484
可愛的女人 她知道你和她兒子 關係有多好
Lovely woman. She knows how close you and her son were.

567
00:47:41,554 --> 00:47:42,954
他在家信中常提起你
He wrote home about you.

568
00:47:43,024 --> 00:47:45,584
她是如此如此地想見到你
She is very, very much looking forward to meeting you.

569
00:47:45,654 --> 00:47:47,754
漢克不在照片
Hank wasn't in the picture.

570
00:47:48,824 --> 00:47:50,024
什麼？
Sorry?

571
00:47:50,894 --> 00:47:53,024
漢克沒有升那面旗
Hank didn't raise that flag.

572
00:47:53,434 --> 00:47:55,694
他升的是另一面 真正的那面
He raised the other one, the real flag.

573
00:47:55,764 --> 00:47:59,294
什麼？ 真正的… 真正的那面？還有這個說法？
The what? The real... The real flag? There's a real flag?

574
00:47:59,374 --> 00:48:00,934
是的 我們升的那面不過是 一面替補旗
Yeah, ours was the replacement flag.

575
00:48:01,004 --> 00:48:03,374
第一面降下去以後我們就 把它升起來了
We put it up when they took the other one down.

576
00:48:03,444 --> 00:48:06,204
你們還有誰覺得頭大的？ 你知道這個麼？
Am I the only one getting a headache here? You know about this?

577
00:48:06,274 --> 00:48:08,304
登報以後我才知道的
It was after it was already in the papers.

578
00:48:08,384 --> 00:48:09,814
母親們都已經接到通知了 不過…
The mothers had already been told, but...

579
00:48:09,884 --> 00:48:13,014
很好 多好啊 好 太好了
That's it, that's beautiful. Yeah, that's beautiful.

580
00:48:13,084 --> 00:48:14,244
那 為什麼告訴我這些？
Yeah, why tell me?

581
00:48:14,324 --> 00:48:16,984
我是不是必須向1億5千萬美國人
I'm only the guy that has to explain it to 150 million Americans.

582
00:48:17,054 --> 00:48:18,784
解釋清楚誰在那該死的照片上？
Who is in the goddamn picture?

583
00:48:18,854 --> 00:48:20,824
你們埵酗H在 那張該死的照片上麼？
Are any of you guys in the goddamn picture?

584
00:48:20,894 --> 00:48:22,794
是的 我們在那張該死的照片上
Yeah, we're in the goddamn picture.

585
00:48:22,864 --> 00:48:25,954
六個人在硫磺島上升起國旗 勝利屬於我們
Six guys raising a flag over lwo Jima. Victory is ours.

586
00:48:26,034 --> 00:48:27,434
你們是其中三個 是麼?
You're three of them, right?

587
00:48:27,504 --> 00:48:30,594
那是第5天發生的事 先生 後來又打了35天
This was the fifth day, sir. The battle went on for 35 more.

588
00:48:30,674 --> 00:48:33,904
那你們當時都做了些什麼？每天 午飯前都升一遍這該死的旗麼？
Well, what'd you do, raise a goddamn flag every time you stopped for lunch?

589
00:48:33,974 --> 00:48:35,564
我能不能打他一頓?
Can I hit this guy?

590
00:48:35,644 --> 00:48:38,074
別的我才不管呢 你們在照片
You know what, I don't give a shit, you're in the picture,

591
00:48:38,144 --> 00:48:40,704
你們把旗升起來了 我們就是想說這個故事
you raised the flag, that's the story we're selling, boys.

592
00:48:40,784 --> 00:48:44,474
你耳朵聾了麼? 漢克不在照片上 哈倫才在照片上
Are you deaf? Hank isn't in the picture. Harlon is in the picture.

593
00:48:44,554 --> 00:48:46,244
那哈倫又他媽是誰？
Well, who the fuck is Harlon?

594
00:48:46,314 --> 00:48:50,554
哈倫·布勞克 他媽媽才應該被邀請
Harlon Block. That's whose mother should be here if anyone's should be.

595
00:48:50,994 --> 00:48:54,894
要我說 這整個事情就是一場鬧劇
You know, I think this whole damn thing is a farce, you ask me.

596
00:49:14,284 --> 00:49:16,844
你知道他們怎麼稱呼這次巡迴籌款麼？ 叫做「偉大的第七屆」巡迴籌款
You know what they're calling this bond drive? The Mighty Seventh.

597
00:49:16,914 --> 00:49:17,944
其實他們本來是想叫
They might've called it the

598
00:49:18,014 --> 00:49:19,784
一群連子彈都買不起的窮光蛋
"We're Flat Fucking Broke And Can't Even Afford Bullets

599
00:49:19,854 --> 00:49:21,484
向您討錢巡迴籌款的
"So We're Begging For Your Pennies" bond drive,

600
00:49:21,554 --> 00:49:24,384
要不是這次籌款數額巨大 他們還真會那麼稱呼這次巡講
but it didn't have quite the ring. They could've called it that, though,

601
00:49:24,454 --> 00:49:26,444
前四屆巡迴籌款都失敗了
because the last four bond drives came up so short

602
00:49:26,524 --> 00:49:28,614
所以我們最後加印了點鈔票了事
we just printed money instead.

603
00:49:28,694 --> 00:49:30,854
在華爾街上隨便問一個聰明人 他都會告訴你
Ask any smart boy on Wall Street, he'll tell you

604
00:49:30,934 --> 00:49:34,094
我們的美元跟紙一樣 我們的欠債堆積如山
our dollar is next to worthless, we borrowed so much.

605
00:49:34,164 --> 00:49:37,004
而且沒人再借給我們了 艦船停造
And nobody is lending any more. Ships aren't being built.

606
00:49:37,074 --> 00:49:40,874
坦克停造 機槍 火箭筒 手榴彈 甚至拉鏈 統統停造
Tanks aren't being built. Machine guns, bazookas, hand grenades, zip.

607
00:49:40,944 --> 00:49:44,034
你覺得這是場鬧劇？ 你想回去見你的戰友們是麼？
You think this is a farce? You want to go back to your buddies?

608
00:49:44,114 --> 00:49:46,574
那上飛機之前 在口袋埵h裝點石頭
Well, stuff some rocks in your pockets before you get on the plane

609
00:49:46,644 --> 00:49:48,944
因為我們只有用那個去扔日本人了
because that's all we got left to throw at the Japanese.

610
00:49:49,014 --> 00:49:51,444
飛機起飛不了你也別奇怪
And don't be surprised if your plane doesn't make it off the runway

611
00:49:51,514 --> 00:49:53,244
因為油箱早空了
because the fuel dumps are empty.

612
00:49:53,324 --> 00:49:56,054
我們的好朋友阿拉伯人 又只肯接受黃金
And our good friends, the Arabs, are only taking bullion.

613
00:49:56,124 --> 00:49:58,454
如果我們這次籌不到140億美元
If we don't raise $14 billion,

614
00:49:58,524 --> 00:50:02,224
我們就全完了 戰爭這個月底就會結束
and that's million with a "B," this war is over by the end of the month.

615
00:50:02,294 --> 00:50:04,784
我們跟日本人談判 他們要求什麼我們給什麼
We make a deal with the Japanese, we give whatever they want

616
00:50:04,864 --> 00:50:06,764
然後我們就回家 因為我們看到 他們戰鬥過了
and we come home, because you've seen them fight,

617
00:50:06,834 --> 00:50:09,194
而且還堅定不移
and they sure as shit ain't giving up.

618
00:50:09,264 --> 00:50:10,964
140億美元
$14 billion.

619
00:50:11,034 --> 00:50:14,234
前三屆加起來都沒有這麼多
The last three drives didn't make that much all together.

620
00:50:16,744 --> 00:50:18,044
街頭巷尾的人們
People on the street corners,

621
00:50:18,114 --> 00:50:21,344
看到這張照片以後 就會重燃希望
they looked at this picture and they took hope.

622
00:50:21,414 --> 00:50:23,504
別問我原因 我覺得這就是張垃圾照片
Don't ask me why, I think it's a crappy picture myself.

623
00:50:23,584 --> 00:50:26,054
連個正臉都看不到
You can't even see your faces.

624
00:50:26,114 --> 00:50:29,954
但它告訴我們 我們可以贏得 並且正在贏得這場戰爭
But it said we can win this war, are winning this war,

625
00:50:30,024 --> 00:50:32,324
我們就只是需要你們 把它的意義深挖一下
we just need you to dig a little deeper.

626
00:50:32,394 --> 00:50:34,054
他們是想把錢給我們麼
They want to give us that money.

627
00:50:34,124 --> 00:50:36,114
不 他們想把錢給你們
No, they want to give it to you.

628
00:50:36,194 --> 00:50:38,994
但是你們 你們不願意要他們的錢 你們不願意給他們希望
But you, you don't want to ask for it. You don't want to give them hope.

629
00:50:39,064 --> 00:50:42,394
你們只是想解釋 什麼這個人啦那面旗啊之類的事情
You want to explain about this person and that flag.

630
00:50:43,064 --> 00:50:45,124
選擇權在你們
Well, that's your choice.

631
00:50:45,874 --> 00:50:49,704
如果我們承認照片出錯 人們就會議論紛紛
Because if we admit we made a mistake, that's all anybody'll talk about

632
00:50:49,774 --> 00:50:51,674
整個計劃就全完了
and that will be that.

633
00:51:01,384 --> 00:51:02,544
先生們
Gentlemen.

634
00:51:04,354 --> 00:51:06,294
總統先生 他們來了
Mr. President, here they are.

635
00:51:06,354 --> 00:51:09,354
嗯 你們好 真高興見到你們 總統先生
Well, hello. Good to see you. Mr. President.

636
00:51:09,424 --> 00:51:10,914
見到你們真高興
Darn good to see you, boys.

637
00:51:10,994 --> 00:51:13,934
聽說你們打了不少硬仗 惡仗是麼
Heard you had a hell of a fight on your hands out there, hell of a fight.

638
00:51:14,004 --> 00:51:15,124
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

639
00:51:15,204 --> 00:51:18,724
艾拉 你是從亞利桑那州 吉拉河保留地來的 是麼？
Ira, you're off the Gila River Reservation in Arizona, am I right?

640
00:51:18,804 --> 00:51:20,604
是的 總統先生
Yes, Mr. President.

641
00:51:20,674 --> 00:51:24,234
作為印第安人 你比我們都更像一個美國人
Being an Indian, you are a truer American than any of us.

642
00:51:24,774 --> 00:51:27,114
你的族人應該會為你身上 的制服感到自豪吧
Bet your people are proud to see you wear that uniform.

643
00:51:27,184 --> 00:51:28,574
非常自豪 先生
Very proud, sir.

644
00:51:29,084 --> 00:51:30,204
理應如此
They should be.

645
00:51:30,284 --> 00:51:33,984
謝謝你們不遠千里來華盛頓幫忙
Well, I want to thank you for coming all this way to Washington to help us out.

646
00:51:34,054 --> 00:51:35,884
你們曾經拿下了太平洋上的敵山
You fought for a mountain in the Pacific

647
00:51:35,954 --> 00:51:38,924
現在我要你們去拿下錢山
now we need you to fight for a mountain of cash.

648
00:51:38,994 --> 00:51:41,654
希望你們不會讓我失望 不會的 先生
And I don't expect you'll let us down. No, sir.

649
00:51:41,724 --> 00:51:43,594
很好 去做吧
Good. Go get it.

650
00:51:43,864 --> 00:51:45,884
儀式到此結束
That's the end of this ceremony.

651
00:51:45,964 --> 00:51:50,404
我們來這兒看看這張照片吧 看我能不能把你們一個個分辨出來
Let's take a look at this famous photo over here, see if I can pick you out.

652
00:51:50,474 --> 00:51:52,874
啊呀 這不是你麼
My gosh. There you are.

653
00:52:01,844 --> 00:52:06,344
小伙們 小伙們 這杯算我的 敬那些死去的戰友
Boys. Boys, this one's on me. To those who can't be with us.

654
00:52:07,054 --> 00:52:08,314
是 長官
Yes, sir.

655
00:52:10,954 --> 00:52:14,794
勞駕 蓋格南先生 能拍張照麼？
Excuse me, Mr. Gagnon. May we have your autograph?

656
00:52:16,424 --> 00:52:17,694
可以啊
I suppose.

657
00:52:18,934 --> 00:52:20,694
你叫什麼名字？
And your name is?

658
00:52:21,234 --> 00:52:22,894
不知你們怎麼想的 我是覺得
I don't know about you, but I get the impression

659
00:52:22,964 --> 00:52:24,734
我好像陪錯英雄了
I'm drinking with the wrong heroes.

660
00:52:24,804 --> 00:52:28,794
你真是一個英雄 和你在一起真令我榮幸
You're such a hero. I feel honored to be in your presence.

661
00:52:29,274 --> 00:52:30,864
哪堶
That's just not true.

662
00:52:33,644 --> 00:52:37,014
演的多專業啊 來 敬演技派一杯
That's professional work. Here, to professionals.

663
00:52:47,494 --> 00:52:50,224
在這兒 你們就是照片上的那幾個人 對吧？
Here they are. You're the guys in the photograph, right?

664
00:52:50,294 --> 00:52:51,884
我聽說你們在車上
I heard you were on the train.

665
00:52:51,964 --> 00:52:53,864
握握手 我是約翰·田納科
Let me shake your hands, John Tennack.

666
00:52:53,934 --> 00:52:55,664
我是約翰·佈雷德利
John Bradley.

667
00:52:55,734 --> 00:52:58,534
這幾個是和我一起的 剛從哈佛和耶魯畢業 都是乳臭未乾的小字輩
These boys are with me, Harvard and Yale types, didn't fight a lick.

668
00:52:58,604 --> 00:53:00,334
他們的老爸都是大富翁
Pappies all rich sons-of-bitches.

669
00:53:00,404 --> 00:53:02,844
跟真正的戰爭英雄握個手吧
Boys, shake hands with some real war heroes.

670
00:53:02,904 --> 00:53:04,604
我先失陪一會兒
Excuse me for one moment.

671
00:53:05,114 --> 00:53:06,734
你不給他們買杯喝的麼
You can buy them a drink while you're at it.

672
00:53:06,814 --> 00:53:09,744
是啊 整個巡迴期間的飲料費我請
That's right. Drinks for these men all the way around.

673
00:53:09,814 --> 00:53:12,414
你就是另外一個 是吧？ 我是約翰·田納科
And you're the other one, aren't you? John Tennack, Tennack Homes.

674
00:53:12,514 --> 00:53:14,544
我是瑞尼·蓋格南 很高興見到你
Rene Gagnon. Pleased to meet you.

675
00:53:14,624 --> 00:53:17,314
喝點什麼吧 來吧 這是我的名片
Have a drink, come on. And here's my card.

676
00:53:17,394 --> 00:53:19,254
聽我說 瑞尼
Listen to me, Rene,

677
00:53:19,324 --> 00:53:22,054
巡講結束 你出了名以後 只管來找我
when you get finished being famous you come see me

678
00:53:22,124 --> 00:53:24,964
因為如果你能賣債券 你就能賣房子
because if you can sell bonds, you can sell homes.

679
00:53:25,034 --> 00:53:28,294
現在他們早就不建造房子了 改成配送房子了
Now, they're not gonna build homes anymore, they're gonna deliver them.

680
00:53:28,364 --> 00:53:30,164
你聽說過活動房屋麼？ 沒有 先生
You heard of prefab homes? No, sir.

681
00:53:30,234 --> 00:53:34,224
你會的 留著名片 到時候來找我 明白麼？
Well, you will. And you hang on to that card and you come see me, you hear?

682
00:53:34,304 --> 00:53:36,104
好麼？肯定的
All right? Certainly will.

683
00:53:43,984 --> 00:53:45,314
好的
All right.

684
00:53:53,524 --> 00:53:55,724
我這算是表態了吧 醫生
This sure takes it, huh, Doc?

685
00:53:57,264 --> 00:54:00,134
如果麥克他們能看見我們的話
If Mike and the guys could see us.

686
00:54:01,334 --> 00:54:03,894
是啊 他們肯定覺得難以置信
Yeah, they'd hardly believe it, would they?

687
00:54:06,374 --> 00:54:07,774
哈倫！
Harlon!

688
00:54:10,974 --> 00:54:12,374
富蘭克林！
Franklin!

689
00:54:16,044 --> 00:54:18,444
你能想像富蘭克林
Can you imagine Franklin

690
00:54:19,754 --> 00:54:21,554
就在這輛火車
on this train

691
00:54:22,724 --> 00:54:27,714
用全銀的餐具在餐車吃東西麼
eating at the dining car with all the silver?

692
00:54:32,134 --> 00:54:34,254
我們不應該在這 醫生
We shouldn't be here, Doc.

693
00:55:09,804 --> 00:55:13,534
（歌詞）主的節日即將來臨
There's gonna be a Hallelujah Day

694
00:55:13,604 --> 00:55:17,444
在外的青年回到家園
When the boys have all come home to stay

695
00:55:17,514 --> 00:55:21,414
萬千樂隊一齊奏響
And a million bands begin to play

696
00:55:21,484 --> 00:55:25,004
我們跳起勝利波爾卡
We'll be dancing the Victory Polka

697
00:55:25,084 --> 00:55:29,024
當我們點起自由的火炬
And when we've lit the torch of liberty

698
00:55:29,084 --> 00:55:31,574
照亮遠方那昏睡的大地
In each blacked-out land across the sea

699
00:55:31,654 --> 00:55:35,054
艾拉！ 嘿 艾拉！ 聽說那張照片是擺拍的
Ira! Hey, Ira! We heard the picture was posed!

700
00:55:35,124 --> 00:55:36,154
什麼？
What?

701
00:55:36,224 --> 00:55:38,454
聽說那張照片是擺拍的！
We heard you posed the picture!

702
00:55:38,534 --> 00:55:39,794
嘿 醫生！
Hey, Doc!

703
00:55:47,974 --> 00:55:50,204
我們真了不起 醫生！
We're bigger than life, Doc!

704
00:55:50,274 --> 00:55:51,864
當女孩和男孩分手
And we'll heave a mighty sigh

705
00:55:51,944 --> 00:55:55,714
我們發出沉重的嘆息
When each gal can kiss the boy she kissed goodbye

706
00:55:55,784 --> 00:55:59,474
他們邁過第五街
And they'll come marching down Fifth Avenue

707
00:55:59,554 --> 00:56:03,754
聯合國來把他們檢閱
The United Nations in review

708
00:56:03,824 --> 00:56:07,524
當夢想終於成真
When this lovely dream has all come true

709
00:56:07,594 --> 00:56:13,654
我們跳起勝利波爾卡
We'll be dancing the Victory Polka

710
00:56:18,234 --> 00:56:19,334
幹得漂亮
Good job.

711
00:56:19,404 --> 00:56:20,564
謝謝
Thank you.

712
00:56:29,544 --> 00:56:31,104
謝謝 女孩們
Thank you, girls!

713
00:56:31,184 --> 00:56:32,584
現在
And now,

714
00:56:33,624 --> 00:56:37,074
這奡N有大家期待已久的人
here are the men you've been waiting to meet,

715
00:56:37,154 --> 00:56:39,024
能帶來好運的人
the men in white.

716
00:56:39,094 --> 00:56:43,114
在我身後的人們 就是硫磺島的英雄們！
Right behind me here, the heroes of lwo Jima,

717
00:56:43,194 --> 00:56:46,634
一等兵瑞尼·蓋格南
Private First Class Rene Gagnon,

718
00:56:46,694 --> 00:56:49,134
一等兵艾拉·海因斯
Private First Class Ira Hayes,

719
00:56:49,204 --> 00:56:52,534
還有海軍醫務兵約翰·佈雷德利
and Navy Corpsman John "Doc" Bradley!

720
00:57:04,984 --> 00:57:06,384
謝謝
Thank you.

721
00:57:10,594 --> 00:57:14,084
很高興大家在晚上來到這 支持我們
It's good of you people to come out tonight in support of the war effort.

722
00:57:14,164 --> 00:57:16,784
我們確實需要你們購買債券 這是一定的
We really need you to buy bonds, that's for sure.

723
00:57:16,864 --> 00:57:19,524
沒有你們的幫助 我們就不能贏得戰爭
'Cause we can't win the war without your help.

724
00:57:19,594 --> 00:57:23,224
儘管我們被人稱為硫磺島英雄
As far as us being the heroes of lwo Jima,

725
00:57:24,274 --> 00:57:25,964
但那不是事實
that's just not the case.

726
00:57:26,634 --> 00:57:28,574
我們其實沒做什麼
We really didn't do much at all.

727
00:57:28,644 --> 00:57:30,234
尤其是他…
Especially him.

728
00:57:30,974 --> 00:57:32,464
尤其是我
Especially me.

729
00:57:33,344 --> 00:57:35,874
我只是個通信兵 就這麼簡單
I was just a runner. That's it.

730
00:57:37,154 --> 00:57:38,914
我們升起了一面旗子
We put up a flag.

731
00:57:38,984 --> 00:57:42,814
旗桿很重 所以我們有好幾個人
The pole we attached it to was heavy, so it took a number of us.

732
00:57:42,884 --> 00:57:45,184
我們正巧在升旗的時候 被拍了下來
We had our picture taken doing it.

733
00:57:46,254 --> 00:57:49,994
真正的英雄 已經死在了那座小島上
The real heroes are dead on that island.

734
00:57:50,534 --> 00:57:54,094
如果你們踴躍購買債券來紀念他們 我們將會非常感激 謝謝
And we'd appreciate it if you bought bonds in honor of them. Thank you.

735
00:58:11,554 --> 00:58:13,574
你身邊爆炸過手榴彈麼 艾拉？
Jump on any grenades, Ira?

736
00:58:14,224 --> 00:58:17,344
你像我一樣端掉過碉堡麼？
Take out any machine gun nests I missed?

737
00:58:17,424 --> 00:58:19,894
起碼我還開過槍
At least I fired my weapon.

738
00:58:19,954 --> 00:58:21,294
你得了吧
All right, knock it off.

739
00:58:21,364 --> 00:58:23,294
你打中過什麼？ 當時你是不是喝多了？
You hit anything or were you too drunk then, too?

740
00:58:23,364 --> 00:58:24,454
你說什麼？
What?

741
00:58:25,094 --> 00:58:27,194
別！停手！
Guys! Come on!

742
00:58:27,264 --> 00:58:29,594
停手 別來了
Stop it. Knock it off.

743
00:58:49,424 --> 00:58:54,184
（歌詞）戴高帽的高個男人 站在路中央
The tall man with the high hat will be coming down your way

744
00:58:54,264 --> 00:58:57,424
聽到他的叫嚷 就趕緊把存款取出銀行
Get your savings out when you hear him shout

745
00:58:57,494 --> 00:58:59,964
「買債券麼?」
"Any bonds today?"

746
00:59:00,034 --> 00:59:02,964
買債券麼?
Any bonds today?

747
00:59:03,034 --> 00:59:05,524
我銷售的是自由的債券
Bonds of freedom that's what I'm selling

748
00:59:05,604 --> 00:59:06,934
買債券麼?
Any bonds today?

749
00:59:07,004 --> 00:59:10,374
瑞尼 這 坐在他們兩個人中間
Rene, right here. Sit between these two boys.

750
00:59:11,014 --> 00:59:13,774
（歌詞）自由之人現在降臨
Here comes the freedom man

751
00:59:13,844 --> 00:59:18,904
請你今天為自由買一份單
Asking you to buy a share of freedom today

752
00:59:21,454 --> 00:59:24,214
他們需要我們的幫助
...for us and they need our help.

753
00:59:24,694 --> 00:59:28,684
如果你真的去想的話 你就會發現
And, if you think about it, I think you'll realize

754
00:59:28,764 --> 00:59:33,694
購買更多的債券 不只是一件正確的事
that buying more bonds is not just the right thing to do

755
00:59:33,964 --> 00:59:35,864
也是你唯一能做的事
but the only thing to do.

756
00:59:37,504 --> 00:59:40,524
是的 戰爭已經持續了太久
Yes, this war has gone on too long.

757
00:59:41,744 --> 00:59:45,674
生命已經付出了太多 它的代價…
We have given too many lives. And its cost...

758
00:59:45,744 --> 00:59:48,074
要淋巧克力還是草莓 草莓
Chocolate or strawberry, sir? Strawberry.

759
00:59:48,144 --> 00:59:50,514
…已經是那麼的高昂
...has been far too high.

760
00:59:50,584 --> 00:59:52,484
但如果我們現在動搖
But if we waver now,

761
00:59:52,554 --> 00:59:57,314
如果我們不再竭盡所能 傾盡全力
if we don't dig deep and give more than we think we can

762
00:59:57,394 --> 01:00:00,454
那麼之前的所有犧牲 就全都白費了
then those sacrifices would be wasted...

763
01:00:00,524 --> 01:00:01,924
要淋巧克力還是草莓 先生？
Chocolate or strawberry, sir?

764
01:00:01,994 --> 01:00:04,554
所有那些逝去的生命 就全都只是徒勞了
...and those lives lost in vain.

765
01:01:43,294 --> 01:01:46,324
行動！ 上 上！
Let's move! Go, go!

766
01:02:08,224 --> 01:02:11,054
六號 我是二號 完畢 坦克都到哪去了？
Easy Six, this is Easy Two, over. Where the hell are our tanks?

767
01:02:11,124 --> 01:02:13,684
陷在沙子堣F 上尉說沒有坦克我們也得上
Stuck in the sand. Captain says you're to go without them.

768
01:02:13,754 --> 01:02:15,054
天啊
Christ.

769
01:02:15,624 --> 01:02:18,494
你幹得可真不錯啊 瑞尼
That's real good work you're doing there, Rene.

770
01:02:20,134 --> 01:02:22,254
好的 準備行動 傳話下去
All right, prepare to move out. Pass the word.

771
01:02:22,334 --> 01:02:25,094
二排！ 行動 行動 行動！
Second Platoon! Move! Move! Move!

772
01:02:25,174 --> 01:02:28,534
好 二排 動身！ 行動！
All right, Second Platoon, on your feet! Let's move out!

773
01:02:28,604 --> 01:02:29,934
你個蠢驢
Jackass.

774
01:02:30,004 --> 01:02:31,604
行動！
Let's move out!

775
01:02:33,374 --> 01:02:36,174
上 上！ 上 上 上！
Go, go! Move, move, move!

776
01:02:39,054 --> 01:02:40,484
醫務兵！
Corpsman!

777
01:02:52,334 --> 01:02:53,954
醫務兵！
Corpsman!

778
01:02:55,864 --> 01:02:58,334
二排 行動！
Second Platoon, move out!

779
01:03:03,204 --> 01:03:04,364
醫生！
Doc!

780
01:03:05,614 --> 01:03:07,514
醫生 離開那兒！
Doc, get out of there!

781
01:03:16,024 --> 01:03:17,614
醫務兵！
Corpsman!

782
01:03:18,554 --> 01:03:19,814
醫生！
Doc!

783
01:03:28,104 --> 01:03:29,964
醫生 趕緊給我離開那兒！
Doc, get the hell out of there!

784
01:03:36,744 --> 01:03:39,174
大家請注意
May I have your attention, please.

785
01:03:39,244 --> 01:03:44,914
開往紐約城 波士頓
Train number 48 with service from New York City, Boston,

786
01:03:44,984 --> 01:03:48,854
紐約州羅徹斯特市
Rochester, New York,

787
01:03:48,924 --> 01:03:53,294
俄亥俄州托萊多市和印第安納州南本德市的 第48次列車 現已在第7道進站
Toledo, Ohio, and South Bend, Indiana is now arriving on Track 7.

788
01:03:53,354 --> 01:03:57,354
第48次列車現已在第7道進站
Train number 48 now arriving on Track number 7.

789
01:03:57,434 --> 01:03:59,454
好 下車吧 下車
Okay, let's go. Let's go.

790
01:04:02,964 --> 01:04:04,994
來吧 走
Come on, boys. Let's go.

791
01:04:05,474 --> 01:04:07,834
腳下留神 太太 謝謝
Watch your step, ma'am. Thank you very much.

792
01:04:28,864 --> 01:04:32,664
女士們先生們 在此我謹向大家介紹 硫磺島的英雄們
Ladies and gentlemen, may I present the heroes of lwo Jima.

793
01:04:35,204 --> 01:04:37,964
海軍醫務兵 綽號「醫生」 約翰·佈雷德利
Navy Corpsman John "Doc" Bradley.

794
01:04:40,134 --> 01:04:43,004
一等兵艾拉·海因斯
Private First Class Ira Hayes.

795
01:04:44,174 --> 01:04:46,904
一等兵瑞尼·蓋格南
And Private First Class Rene Gagnon.

796
01:04:47,984 --> 01:04:50,214
瑞尼  那是我男朋友
Rene! That's my boyfriend!

797
01:04:51,954 --> 01:04:53,884
那人是誰
Who the hell is that?

798
01:04:53,954 --> 01:04:55,314
不知道
I don't know.

799
01:04:55,384 --> 01:04:57,374
瑞尼  她是你女朋友麼 嘿 他們叫你什麼
Rene, is that your girl? Hey, what do they call you?

800
01:04:57,454 --> 01:05:00,014
來一張怎麼樣  嘿 看看！
How about a photo? Hey, look at that!

801
01:05:02,594 --> 01:05:04,854
你叫什麼 小美人 你叫什麼名字
What's your name, doll? What's your name?

802
01:05:04,934 --> 01:05:06,694
嘿  她可真是個美人兒
Hey, she's a beauty.

803
01:05:13,234 --> 01:05:15,174
我們去找個沙龍吧
Let's go find a saloon.

804
01:05:25,714 --> 01:05:28,444
大家笑一笑 讓他們覺得物有所值
Smile, boys. Give them their money's worth.

805
01:05:29,724 --> 01:05:32,414
嘿 醫生 一路下來感覺如何?
Hey, Doc, how's the tour going for you?

806
01:05:34,124 --> 01:05:35,214
謝謝
Thank you.

807
01:05:35,294 --> 01:05:36,884
你知道自己現在在哪婸
Where exactly are you staying?

808
01:05:36,964 --> 01:05:39,364
我還不確定… 那就忘了那回事吧
I'm not sure yet. Just forget about that.

809
01:05:51,674 --> 01:05:53,874
參議員先生 這位是 醫務兵約翰·佈雷德利
Senator, I'd like you to meet Corpsman John Bradley.

810
01:05:53,944 --> 01:05:55,674
這就是醫生 是吧 是的 很高興見到您 參議員先生
Doc, right? Yes, sir. Nice to meet you, Senator.

811
01:05:55,744 --> 01:05:57,214
真高興見到你 年輕人
Good to meet you, young man.

812
01:05:57,284 --> 01:06:00,114
感謝你一直以來的所作所為
Now, we appreciate everything you've done and everything you're doing.

813
01:06:00,184 --> 01:06:01,944
謝謝你 先生 不算什麼
Thank you, sir. Quite all right.

814
01:06:02,024 --> 01:06:03,644
懷特中校
This is Captain White.

815
01:06:04,624 --> 01:06:06,854
約翰上校 我們為你驕傲 醫務兵
Colonel Johns. We're proud of you, Corpsman.

816
01:06:06,924 --> 01:06:08,484
這是麥克考特尼上校
And then Colonel McCourtney.

817
01:06:08,564 --> 01:06:10,964
格林將軍 很高興見到你
Major General Green. Nice to meet you.

818
01:06:14,064 --> 01:06:16,034
參議員先生 這是一等兵艾拉·海因斯
Senator, this is Private First Class Ira Hayes.

819
01:06:16,104 --> 01:06:17,464
當然
Of course!

820
01:06:17,904 --> 01:06:21,564
我聽說你用印第安戰斧殺那些 日本鬼子 是麼 酋長
Now I hear you used a tomahawk on those Japs. Is that true, Chief?

821
01:06:21,644 --> 01:06:23,104
不是  先生
No, sir.

822
01:06:23,174 --> 01:06:26,234
你說是不就完了嘛  這樣故事才 更好聽嘛
Well, tell them you did, makes a better story, huh?

823
01:06:27,814 --> 01:06:29,904
幹的漂亮 這是格林中校
Attaboy. This is Captain Green.

824
01:06:31,754 --> 01:06:32,944
約翰？
John?

825
01:06:33,414 --> 01:06:37,414
我是麥德琳·艾薇爾 我是從照片上認出你來的 我是漢克的媽媽
Madeline Evelley. I recognize you from all the photographs. I'm Hank's mom.

826
01:06:38,754 --> 01:06:42,384
真高興見到您 夫人 漢克總是提起您
It's so nice to meet you, ma'am. Hank was always talking about you.

827
01:06:42,464 --> 01:06:44,924
這是一等兵瑞尼·蓋格南
This is PFC Rene Gagnon.

828
01:06:44,994 --> 01:06:47,794
很高興認識你 謝謝你
Pleasure to meet you, son. Thanks for everything.

829
01:06:47,864 --> 01:06:49,694
那是我的榮幸 哪堶
My pleasure. Not at all.

830
01:06:50,064 --> 01:06:54,064
艾拉  這是斯坦克太太 麥克的媽媽
Ira, I'd like you to meet Mrs. Strank, Mike's mom.

831
01:07:08,524 --> 01:07:10,044
這沒什麼
It's all right.

832
01:07:10,854 --> 01:07:13,384
接到電報以後  我…
When I got the telegram, I...

833
01:07:14,694 --> 01:07:17,324
不知來這婺蚖”リ偵
I don't know what I'm trying to say here.

834
01:07:19,064 --> 01:07:23,594
知道他那天和你們在一起 看到他出現在那張照片上
Knowing he was with you that day and seeing him in that photograph,

835
01:07:24,334 --> 01:07:27,494
我覺得好多了  也說不清為什麼 不過確實是這樣
I don't know why it makes me feel better, but it does.

836
01:07:28,074 --> 01:07:30,904
這很愚蠢是吧 不  不是的
It's so silly, isn't it? No, it's not.

837
01:07:31,814 --> 01:07:34,334
你好麼? 非常感謝
How are you, son? Thank you very much.

838
01:07:34,944 --> 01:07:38,574
我們是伊利諾伊州最大的 傢俱批發商
We're the largest furniture wholesaler in Illinois.

839
01:07:38,654 --> 01:07:40,444
謝謝 勞駕
Thank you. Excuse me.

840
01:07:41,084 --> 01:07:44,054
（波琳:）我們會打電話給你的 謝謝  謝謝
I'll make sure he calls. Well, thank you. Thank you.

841
01:07:45,424 --> 01:07:46,854
你就是瑞尼麼
Are you Rene?

842
01:07:47,594 --> 01:07:48,894
是的 夫人
Yes, ma'am.

843
01:07:53,634 --> 01:07:55,424
我是富蘭克林的母親
I'm Franklin's mother.

844
01:07:59,274 --> 01:08:01,564
很榮幸見到您  夫人
It's an honor to meet you, ma'am.

845
01:08:03,504 --> 01:08:05,774
我是波琳  瑞尼的女朋友
I'm Pauline, Rene's girlfriend.

846
01:08:08,084 --> 01:08:09,674
你不介意吧
Would you mind?

847
01:08:17,594 --> 01:08:19,454
報紙上說那就是漢克
Paper said that's Hank,

848
01:08:20,424 --> 01:08:22,484
老實說我可沒看出來
and I honestly can't tell.

849
01:08:23,194 --> 01:08:26,964
作為一個母親連她自己的兒子 都認不出來太說不過去了 是吧
It's horrible of a mother not to know her own son, isn't it?

850
01:08:27,034 --> 01:08:28,824
但他確實在畫上 是吧
But that's him, isn't it?

851
01:08:31,034 --> 01:08:33,434
嗯 夫人 說實話 當時太突然了
Well, to be honest, ma'am, it happened so quick,

852
01:08:33,504 --> 01:08:34,974
一切就那麼突然發生了
and with everything that was going on

853
01:08:35,044 --> 01:08:37,834
很難記得當時究竟誰站在什麼 位置上了
it's kind of hard to remember who was where.

854
01:08:39,774 --> 01:08:40,974
但是…
But...

855
01:08:43,414 --> 01:08:45,744
是的 我認為… 我認為他當時就站在那兒
Yeah, I think... I think that's where he was.

856
01:08:45,814 --> 01:08:47,344
那是漢克
That's Hank.

857
01:08:47,414 --> 01:08:48,784
謝謝你
Thank you.

858
01:08:49,384 --> 01:08:50,754
不好意思
Excuse me.

859
01:08:52,724 --> 01:08:54,814
您痛失愛子我深表遺憾
I'm so sorry for your loss.

860
01:08:59,134 --> 01:09:00,464
原諒我們
Excuse us.

861
01:09:16,014 --> 01:09:17,674
把他帶出去
Take him outside.

862
01:09:19,684 --> 01:09:20,944
我是波琳
I'm Pauline.

863
01:09:21,024 --> 01:09:24,014
非常高興見到你 很高興見到你
Very nice to meet you. Hi, nice to meet you.

864
01:09:25,624 --> 01:09:28,284
他是我知道的最好的陸戰隊員
He was the best Marine I ever knew.

865
01:09:29,464 --> 01:09:30,824
謝謝
Thank you.

866
01:09:40,534 --> 01:09:43,504
你沒事吧 酋長 老天
You okay, Chief? Oh, Christ!

867
01:09:43,574 --> 01:09:45,094
我沒事
I'm okay.

868
01:09:45,174 --> 01:09:48,874
好啊 你看看你 你想把事情搞砸 是麼
Yeah, you look it. You're gonna screw this up, aren't you?

869
01:09:48,944 --> 01:09:51,314
你想把大家的事全搞砸
You're gonna screw it up for all of us.

870
01:09:52,384 --> 01:09:53,714
我來跟他講
I've got him.

871
01:09:53,784 --> 01:09:55,654
睡一覺吧  艾拉
Get some sleep, Ira.

872
01:11:22,274 --> 01:11:23,674
麥克 什麼事
Mike? Yeah?

873
01:11:24,374 --> 01:11:25,704
看見沒有 什麼
You see this? What?

874
01:11:25,774 --> 01:11:28,114
麥克 糟糕  快上
Mike! Oh, shit, go!

875
01:11:34,454 --> 01:11:36,214
他殺我！
He's killing me!

876
01:12:16,124 --> 01:12:17,994
嘿 醫生 他們被全滅了麼
Hey, Doc, you think they got them all?

877
01:12:18,064 --> 01:12:19,224
什麼
What?

878
01:12:19,734 --> 01:12:22,724
你看他們都不打我們了 可能被我們全殲了吧
Well, they're not shooting at us. Maybe we killed them all.

879
01:12:22,804 --> 01:12:24,204
要不然就是他們連夜逃跑了吧
Or they ran off in the night or something.

880
01:12:24,264 --> 01:12:26,204
再不然他們在等我們開始爬山
Or they're waiting for us to start climbing.

881
01:12:26,274 --> 01:12:29,034
三排！ 拿上傢伙 我們爬那座山去
Third Platoon! Grab your gear, we're going up the hill.

882
01:12:29,104 --> 01:12:31,164
就只有我們？ 是啊 就我們 伊基
Just us? Yeah, just us, lgg.

883
01:12:31,244 --> 01:12:33,804
好的 三排 行動
All right, Third Platoon, move!

884
01:12:33,874 --> 01:12:35,544
我也跟著去？
I tag along?

885
01:12:35,614 --> 01:12:38,814
行啊  願意的話  你走前面 好好給我來幾個特寫
Yeah, you can lead the way if you want. Get a good shot of my face.

886
01:12:38,884 --> 01:12:41,284
給你來個屁股特寫你就能出名
It's your ass I'm gonna make famous, Hank.

887
01:12:41,354 --> 01:12:43,614
嘿 我也是
Hey, that'll work for me, too.

888
01:12:45,924 --> 01:12:47,414
中尉
Lieutenant,

889
01:12:48,064 --> 01:12:50,964
到山頂以後 把這個掛上
if you make it to the top, put this up.

890
01:12:51,024 --> 01:12:52,294
是
Yes, sir.

891
01:12:58,804 --> 01:13:01,394
別擔心 伊基 他們不打排頭兵的
Don't worry, Iggy. They never shoot at the first patrol.

892
01:13:01,474 --> 01:13:03,064
是麼 是啊
They don't? No.

893
01:13:03,574 --> 01:13:06,664
我們肯定安全到頂 因為他們不想打草驚蛇
They want us to go up to the top, signal to the others that it's okay,

894
01:13:06,744 --> 01:13:08,734
等到後續大部隊上山 他們才會大開殺戒
then shoot everybody else as they come up the mountain.

895
01:13:08,814 --> 01:13:10,714
是麼 是啊
Really? Yeah.

896
01:13:10,784 --> 01:13:12,804
除非他們想來個殺雞儆猴
Unless of course they want to make an example of us

897
01:13:12,884 --> 01:13:14,474
先給山下的弟兄一個下馬威
and discourage all the others.

898
01:13:14,554 --> 01:13:17,074
你廢話還真是多 知道麼 漢克
I think you're full of crap, you know that, Hank?

899
01:13:17,154 --> 01:13:18,384
是麼
Really?

900
01:13:19,194 --> 01:13:20,684
老天
Jesus.

901
01:13:22,424 --> 01:13:24,254
幸虧那不是我們
Thank God that ain't us.

902
01:13:36,744 --> 01:13:38,004
早告訴過你我們會沒事吧
Told you.

903
01:13:40,244 --> 01:13:42,774
博茨 讓他們做好防禦
Boots, spread them out and put them on a line.

904
01:13:42,844 --> 01:13:45,614
一班  原地駐防
Set up a perimeter! First Squad!

905
01:13:51,294 --> 01:13:53,194
漢克 找個洞 行
Hank? Find me a pole. Yeah.

906
01:13:56,994 --> 01:13:58,724
我們把旗升起來
Let's put this flag up.

907
01:14:05,534 --> 01:14:06,794
看準了
Watch it.

908
01:14:07,604 --> 01:14:08,934
就這兒
Right over here.

909
01:14:14,374 --> 01:14:16,814
就這兒 很好 很好 這兒 這兒
Right here. That's good. That's good. Right here, right here.

910
01:14:16,884 --> 01:14:19,074
抓住那頭沒有 拿穩了
Got that end? Hold that steady.

911
01:14:20,314 --> 01:14:21,654
林勃
Lindberg.

912
01:14:23,984 --> 01:14:26,114
嘿 誰有繩子 這兒有
Hey, who's got rope? Right here.

913
01:14:30,194 --> 01:14:32,024
給我 對 好
Give me something. Yeah, good.

914
01:14:32,094 --> 01:14:33,324
行麼
That work?

915
01:14:38,174 --> 01:14:39,694
干吧
Do it, fellas.

916
01:14:41,644 --> 01:14:42,974
保持住
Keep it coming.

917
01:14:49,544 --> 01:14:52,814
陸戰隊！陸戰隊！
USMC! USMC!


918
01:14:49,544 --> 01:14:52,814
USMC 為美海軍陸戰隊略稱

919
01:14:53,914 --> 01:14:55,114
靠  看那
Shit, look at that!

920
01:15:29,584 --> 01:15:31,244
天 看那
Jeez, look at that.

921
01:15:39,134 --> 01:15:41,364
臥倒！ 找掩護！
Get down! Take cover!

922
01:15:42,104 --> 01:15:43,364
射擊
Cover with that.30!

923
01:15:43,434 --> 01:15:46,524
當心 下方20碼 漢克！ 看到沒有？
Watch it! Twenty yards down, Hank! You see them?

924
01:15:47,404 --> 01:15:51,104
大約20碼  左側 林勃 去拿噴火器來
I got about 20 yards, left side. Lindberg, get the flamethrower!

925
01:15:52,344 --> 01:15:55,004
博茨 看到沒有 掩護右翼！
Boots, you see them? Cover right!

926
01:15:55,544 --> 01:15:58,344
下方大約20碼 發現一個！ 看到沒有？
About 20 yards down! Duck one! You see them?

927
01:15:58,414 --> 01:16:00,404
繼續掩護
Keep the cover on!

928
01:16:00,484 --> 01:16:02,474
二班 看到沒有？
Second Squad, you see them?

929
01:16:02,884 --> 01:16:04,874
手榴彈給我
Get me some grenades!

930
01:16:04,954 --> 01:16:06,384
看到了
I see them!

931
01:16:17,704 --> 01:16:18,794
你看到了？
You see them?

932
01:16:18,874 --> 01:16:21,064
右翼 轉向左側！
Right flank, over to the right!

933
01:16:24,504 --> 01:16:26,374
掩護我 我下去看看
Cover me, I'm going down!

934
01:16:26,774 --> 01:16:28,004
小心 伊基
Careful, Iggy.

935
01:16:28,084 --> 01:16:29,064
慢點下
Easy.

936
01:16:30,114 --> 01:16:31,104
目標清除
All clear!

937
01:16:40,354 --> 01:16:43,794
好的 小伙們 誰想出名
Okay, guys, who wants to be famous?

938
01:16:46,134 --> 01:16:48,064
是 長官  我立即去辦 長官
Yes, sir. Right away, sir.

939
01:16:48,134 --> 01:16:50,864
他媽的  斯坦克 長官？
God damn it. Strank! Sir?

940
01:16:50,934 --> 01:16:53,334
他們想把電話線架到山頂去
They want a phone line run up to the top of the mountain.

941
01:16:53,404 --> 01:16:55,234
猜就是讓我們去
Let me guess, they picked us.

942
01:16:55,304 --> 01:16:58,204
二排 我們走 運動一下
Second Platoon, let's go. Get some exercise.

943
01:17:03,914 --> 01:17:06,384
走啦  爬起來
Let's go! Get off your ass.

944
01:17:10,484 --> 01:17:12,084
我靠
Oh, shit!

945
01:17:12,454 --> 01:17:15,754
希望它還能用 因為我不會借給你用的
Hope it still works, 'cause you're not getting mine!

946
01:17:16,364 --> 01:17:18,724
我拍到福萊斯特號了！ 好啊
Get Forrestal! All right, then.

947
01:17:22,564 --> 01:17:24,894
我不知道那是誰的主意 參謀長先生
I don't know whose idea it was, Mr. Secretary.

948
01:17:24,974 --> 01:17:29,164
真他媽天才 我想要那面旗 霍蘭
Well, it was goddamn brilliant. I want that flag, Holland.


949
01:17:24,974 --> 01:17:29,164
霍蘭·史密斯 第五兩棲軍軍長 硫磺島地面戰的總指揮

950
01:17:29,244 --> 01:17:31,504
記下我的話 升起那面旗
Mark my words, raising that son-of-a-bitch

951
01:17:31,574 --> 01:17:34,734
意味著陸戰隊能再存在500年
means a Marine Corps for the next 500 years.

952
01:17:35,644 --> 01:17:37,584
我想要那面旗
I want that flag.

953
01:17:38,554 --> 01:17:41,344
是 長官 我會確保沒人動它的
Yes, sir. I'll make sure no one touches it.

954
01:17:41,414 --> 01:17:43,254
相信我
You can count on me.

955
01:17:44,224 --> 01:17:47,854
操他媽的 旗子是屬於全營人的
Fuck that. That flag belongs to the men in this battalion.

956
01:17:47,924 --> 01:17:50,554
那婊子養的還以為 我們提著腦袋打下這
That son-of-a-bitch thinks that our men died taking this ground

957
01:17:50,624 --> 01:17:53,654
就是為了把我們的旗子 送給政客去掛在他牆上麼
so we could hand over our flag to some politician to pin to his wall?

958
01:17:53,734 --> 01:17:55,894
真他媽腦子燒壞了
He's out of his goddamn mind!

959
01:17:56,964 --> 01:17:59,264
把那面旗給我拿下來 另找一面替上它
Get me that flag, and find another one to replace it.

960
01:17:59,334 --> 01:18:01,564
你這不是耍我麼
You've gotta be shitting me.

961
01:18:01,644 --> 01:18:02,904
蓋格南！
Gagnon!

962
01:18:04,274 --> 01:18:06,004
趕緊給我滾過來
Get your ass over here.

963
